data.description: 4 Bedroom 4 bath Two Story Colonial on very large beautifully wooded lot on private Cul-de Sac road. Home features Master Suite, spacious living room, main floor Laundry, Kitchen with maple cabinetry. Off the dinning area a patio door will lead to  deck overlooking backyard with firepit and Kid's playset . 2017 home was updated with new furnace, finished basement with large family room, full bath and bedroom. 2020 new energy efficient windows where installed. 2021 new Refrigerator and Gas Range.,Kid's playset in backyard is included.
